---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/?$/, '/');
---

<section class="intro" id="intro" aria-labelledby="intro-heading">
  <div class="intro__inner">
    <div class="intro__content reveal reveal--drift" style="--drift-x: -16px">
      <h2 id="intro-heading" class="intro__heading">How We Work</h2>
      <p class="intro__text">Owning a boat should be about enjoying the water, not managing a never-ending list of separate contractors, mechanics, and boatyard drop-offs. At Technique Marine, we eliminate the headache by providing a comprehensive, single-source mobile solution for absolutely everything your vessel requires.</p>
      <p class="intro__text">We bring top-tier technique directly to your driveway, slip, or marina across the Carolinas. Whether you need an emergency bilge pump replaced, a complex Garmin NMEA network engineered, an annual Mercury engine service, a full hull detail, or a licensed USCG captain to deliver your yacht down the coast—we have the expertise to handle it. If it's on a boat, we can install it, fix it, clean it, maintain it, or captain it.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="intro__image reveal reveal--drift" style="--drift-x: 24px">
      <img src={`${base}images/boat.jpg`} alt="Boat docked at a marina, reflecting Technique Marine's mobile service area" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .intro {
    background-color: var(--color-cream);
    padding: 80px 24px;
  }

  .intro__inner {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 48px;
  }

  .intro__content {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .intro__heading {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-navy);
  }

  .intro__text {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    line-height: 1.8;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .intro__image {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 360px;
  }

  .intro__image img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-gold);
    display: block;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .intro__inner {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 32px;
    }

    .intro__image {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 360px;
    }
  }
</style>
